enhanced_by.reason: The transform method relies on the Function<MyObject, MyType> provided during the object construction.
The transform method may rely on the Supplier<MyType> provided during the object construction if the Function is null.
The getTransform method returns the same Function<MyObject, MyType> used by the transform method, which can be used to verify the transformation logic.
The getSupplier method returns the same Supplier<MyType> used by the transform method if the Function is null, which can be used to verify the supplier logic.
